{"tid":1688521,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"不如消防處under班黑警算啦","createTime":"2019-11-02T12:46:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-02T17:51:58.000Z","uid":21190,"like":300,"dislike":41,"uniUserReply":53,"replies":[{"pid":"0b559d4a5fa3dc2c2753e2100bb1cc169f4ff6a4","tid":1688521,"uid":21190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T12:46:56.000Z","msg":"依家D消防咁撚垃圾連自己架車都保唔住<br />\n見到自己手足比人蝦到上心口仲可以粒聲唔出<br />\n體能好過班黑警都無用呀<br />\n不如直接under班有晒gear既偽進仔咪算囉<br />\n反正你地都係跟住班黑警指揮嫁啦<br />\n人地叫你行東你都唔敢行西<br />\n仲要貼埋自己局入面架車仔出去比人做野<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港警務處救火小隊</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7590d8bd4fed8dd50b88e18e801a10b257cddd13","tid":1688521,"uid":21190,"like":4,"dislike":5,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T12:50:15.000Z","msg":"消防仔要做班狗仔唔忿氣呀?<br />\n鬼叫你考個陣唔醒爬少少<br />\n好好地考個正牌黑社會咪幾好<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57184d905b38c4b346fbb192615475b57d2ecfea","tid":1688521,"uid":263038,"like":16,"dislike":2,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T12:52:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">以後大家唔好再叫消防員<br />\n係叫香港警務救火員</span></span>"},{"pid":"7db963babd14d7db621b467bcc06b7bd2700d309","tid":1688521,"uid":21190,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"57184d905b38c4b346fbb192615475b57d2ecfea","tid":1688521,"uid":263038,"like":16,"dislike":2,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T12:52:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">以後大家唔好再叫消防員<br />\n係叫香港警務救火員</span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T12:54:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span st